1678956498.text: "In conclusion, we have found that desflurane activated NF-kappaB during the preconditioning period, inhibited excessive activation of NF-kappaB in reperfusion, up-regulated Bcl-2 and c-IAP1 expression and inhibited SMAC release and caspase-3 cleavage after A/R injury."
